Carnage/Teltoli

* It was nearing dawn and Carnage walked on grogily as Teltoli flew on 
ahead, they'd slept but now were moving on to try and find the Maximals.
Carnage stretched her arms and yawned, she was stiff from the cold and her 
stomach felt empty again. She looked up into the sky and smiled up at 
Teltoli.*

" Hay!," she said into her com-link to the Fuzor, " any ideas of where we're 
going?"

* Teltoli looked down at Carnage at the sound of her voice over the intercom 
and smiled to herself.*
Teltoli: " No clue. I'm just flying. I thought that you knew where we were 
going?"

* Carnage shook her head and sighed. Well, that solved that question.
She looked around then stopped, she'd heard something!
Carnage looked around at the surrounding trees and saw nothing, but then 
suddenly a doe sprang from the trees and sprang off into the distance.
Carnage relaxed, nothing serious.*
